	ket limit per patron. Patrons exceeding the ticket limit will have their o
	rders cancelled at the venue's discretion. All sales are final. No refunds
	 or exchanges. Unless otherwise noted\, each person must have a ticket reg
	ardless of age. No babies in arms. Mobile ticket delivery will be delayed 
	until 4 days prior to event.\nMetal detectors & bag search at door. Arrive
	 early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety When purchasing ADA a
	ccessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by email if assistance 
	is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; you may reach us at a
	ccessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat houses an armless frees
	tanding chair for patrons with mobility impairments and their companions. 
	Please note that our historic theatre has no elevator to the balcony level
